OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe NHS did not implement radical
OL,8,Fchange amid repeated complaints about
OL,9,Fmental health care in the years
OL,10,Fleading up to the Nottingham attacks,
OL,11,Fa former ombudsman has told a public
OL,12,Finquiry.
OL,14,FSir Rob Behrens, who was the
OL,15,FParliamentary and Health Service
OL,16,FOmbudsman between April 2017 and March
OL,17,F2024, also told the inquiry that
OL,18,Fbereaved families had "too often" been
OL,19,Fleft to campaign for change.
OL,26,@zD@WOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe inquiry is examining agencies'
OL,8,Finteractions with paranoid
OL,9,Fschizophrenic Valdo Calocane, who
OL,10,Ffatally stabbed university students
OL,11,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,12,FKumar, both 19, and 65-year-old school
OL,13,Fcaretaker Ian Coates in June 2023.
OL,15,FCalocane was ordered to be detained in
OL,16,Fa high-security hospital in 2024
OL,17,Ffollowing his sentencing for
OL,18,Fmanslaughter on the grounds of
OL,19,Fdiminished responsibility and the
OL,20,Fattempted murder of three pedestrians.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FGiving evidence to the inquiry's
OL,8,Fchairwoman, Her Honour Deborah Taylor,
OL,9,Fat the central London hearing on
OL,10,FWednesday, Sir Rob confirmed that
OL,11,Fcomplaints he had received in the role
OL,12,Fof Health Service Ombudsman had
OL,13,Frelated to improper risk assessments
OL,14,Fconcerning public safety and risk to
OL,15,Fothers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSir Rob told the inquiry: "One of the
OL,8,Fkey themes about mental health
OL,9,Fcomplaints throughout my tenure was
OL,10,Fthese issues (highlighted in a report)
OL,11,Fin 2018 arose time and again up until
OL,12,F2024 without effectively being
OL,13,Faddressed, even though we lobbied hard
OL,14,Fto draw attention to these issues."
OL,16,FAsked by inquiry counsel Craig Carr if
OL,17,Fnothing had changed, Sir Rob replied:
OL,18,F"I won't say nothing changed but there
OL,19,Fwasn't a radical change."
OL,26,@oD@[OUvD@cO]zD@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSir Rob, who previously served as
OL,8,Fsecretary to the Committee on
OL,9,FStandards in Public Life, added: "I'm
OL,10,Fconscious that during my tenure as
OL,11,Fombudsman there were 40 different
OL,12,Fministers of health in the
OL,13,Fdepartment... and six different
OL,14,Fsecretaries of state.
OL,16,F"That kind of churn is not conducive
OL,17,Fto a continuous reform and reflection
OL,18,Fconsistently across the piece."
OL,26,@qD@bOUxD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSir Rob also referenced a lack of
OL,8,Fcandour among some health
OL,9,Fprofessionals, telling the inquiry it
OL,10,Fwas a "consistent theme" across his
OL,11,Fseven years in office, which he had
OL,12,Frepeatedly drawn attention to.
OL,14,FThe former ombudsman added: "It is
OL,15,Fshocking.
OL,17,F"I had not expected when I became
OL,18,Fombudsman that public servants would
OL,19,Feither not tell the truth or fail to
OL,20,Fvolunteer the truth about patient
OL,21,Fsafety issues.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@XO]vD@]OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"There are so many disparate cultures
OL,8,Foverlapping with each other... and
OL,9,Factually hiding the fact that there
OL,10,Fare countless numbers of dedicated
OL,11,Fhealth workers in the public service
OL,12,Fwho give their time and commitment to
OL,13,Fpromote patient safety.
OL,15,F"But that sits alongside pockets of
OL,16,Flack of candour, defensiveness, and an
OL,17,Finability to treat complainants as
OL,18,Findividuals who deserve respect and
OL,19,Fintegrity.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"I think in the time that I was in
OL,8,Foffice, there was a lack of
OL,9,Fministerial focus on that issue of
OL,10,Fdefensiveness.
OL,12,F"Too often clinicians ` good
OL,13,Fclinicians ` who brought patient
OL,14,Fsafety issues to the attention of the
OL,15,Fboard (of NHS Trusts) were disciplined
OL,16,Fas a result of doing that and sent to
OL,17,Fthe General Medical Council, which is
OL,18,Foutrageous."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FAsked by Mr Carr if he thought the NHS
OL,8,Fis learning and making changes in
OL,9,Frelation to issues surrounding candour
OL,10,Fand "cover-up" and "burying" the
OL,11,Ftruth, Sir Rob responded: "I think
OL,12,Fit's been very slow.
OL,14,F"I think leadership is a key problem
OL,15,Fin the NHS."
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@NO]rD@TOUrD@\O]sD@[OUvD@AOUwD@
OL,26,ALO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FDuring his evidence, Sir Rob said he
OL,8,Fwas frustrated "time and again" by the
OL,9,Ffact his office's concerns, including
OL,10,Fon the issue of patient safety, were
OL,11,Fnot taken as seriously by ministers as
OL,12,Fhe felt they needed to be.
OL,14,FTim Moloney KC, representing relatives
OL,15,Fof those killed by Calocane, asked the
OL,16,Fwitness if it often fell to victims
OL,17,Fand survivors of a tragedy to campaign
OL,18,Ffor the implementation of the
OL,19,Frecommendations of inquiries such as
OL,20,Fthat into the Nottingham attacks.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSir Rob responded: "This is a very
OL,8,Fserious point. Without the campaigning
OL,9,Fof distressed and vulnerable and
OL,10,Ftraumatised people we would be a lot
OL,11,Ffurther back in addressing the issues
OL,12,Fthat need addressing.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, too often the
OL,15,Fsuccessful resolution of these cases
OL,16,Fhas depended upon bereaved families
OL,17,Fcampaigning at a time when they are
OL,18,Fleast well prepared to do that.
OL,20,F"And it is an outstanding public
OL,21,Fservice that they perform."
OL,26,@oD@TOUvD@AOU|D@AOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FMr Moloney said of survivors and
OL,8,Fvictims' relatives: "Having to
OL,9,Fcampaign to ensure the implementation
OL,10,Fof recommendations necessarily
OL,11,Fcompounds their trauma doesn't it?
OL,12,FThey go through an inquiry, they
OL,13,Fsecure positive recommendations for
OL,14,Fchange, government commit to implement
OL,15,Fin full and then nothing happens. And
OL,16,Ftheir tragedy has to endure in trying
OL,17,Fto secure the implementation?"
OL,19,FSir Rob answered: "That's absolutely
OL,20,Fright... it shouldn't be down to the
OL,21,Ffamilies.
OL,26,@pD@UOUyD@^O]{D@SOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780646725
OL,3,CBereaved families 'too often' forced
OL,4,Cto campaign for change, Nottingham
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"There needs to be an institutional
OL,8,Ffocus for this ` and there isn't at
OL,9,Fthe moment."
OL,11,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@LO]
